Title: Hey Arnold!
Writer: Craig Bartlett, Steve Viksten, Joe Ansolabehere
Actors: Francesca Marie Smith, Jamil Walker Smith, Dan Castellaneta, Justin Shenkarow
Plot: The everyday life of Arnold, a 4th-grader in a nameless city that resembles Brooklyn, New York, who lives in a multi-racial boarding house with his grandparents and a motley assortment of neighbors and friends.
